1. *Bacio* je loptu u daljinu. (*Bacio* - Threw) (He threw the ball far away.)
2. Moramo *baciti* smeće u kontejner. (*Baciti* - Throw) (We have to throw the garbage in the container.)
3. Zaboravio sam *baciti* novac u kasu. (*Baciti* - Put) (I forgot to put the money in the cash register.)
4. Upravo su *bacili* novu kolekciju cipela. (*Bacili* - Released) (They just released a new collection of shoes.)
5. Ne smijemo *baciti* ovaj projekt, trebamo ga dovršiti. (*Baciti* - Abandon) (We must not abandon this project, we need to finish it.)
6. *Bacite* pogled na ovu sliku. (*Bacite* - Take) (Take a look at this picture.)
7. Jeste li *bacili* pogled na vremensku prognozu? (*Bacili* - Checked) (Did you check the weather forecast?)
8. *Baci* ovaj papir u smeće. (*Baci* - Throw) (Throw this paper in the trash.)
9. Nisam siguran gdje da *bacim* ovaj otpad. (*Bacim* - Throw) (I'm not sure where to throw this waste.)
10. *Bacit ću* pogled na taj dokument kasnije. (*Bacit ću* - Take) (I will take a look at that document later.)